parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sidewall Failure of Continental ProContact TX Tires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the sidewall can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The tire blows out or develops a bulge on the sidewall
resulting in loss of air pressure
and potentially causing the vehicle to become unstable or difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the tire sidewall can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities, especially at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rim Damage due to Tire Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The damage to the rim can cause further tire failures, wheel damage, and affect the overall safety and performance of the vehicle.
